column2: For RNA-seq analysis, sequenced reads were trimmed for adaptor sequence, and masked for low-complexity or low-quality sequence, then mapped to GRCh38.p11 annotation using HISAT2 (version 2.1.0) .The Fragments Per Kilobase of transcript per Million mapped reads (FPKM) value of the  transcripts was calculated based on StringTie (version 1.3.4) with default parameters.
